<br>
Mindbogglingly waste of time and energy imho.<br>
<br>
We use the simpliest (sp?) system we could imagine: all get 3 dkp/hour of raiding (sometimes on shit encounters... Rathe .. Xeg .. there is a 5-10 dkp bonus) and on all items dropped there is a quick auction, bids start on 1.<br>
<br>
Pros: Super simple logging: just have a bot doing &quot;/who all GUILD&quot; every hour on the hour. No special rules for anything: highest bidder wins. period.<br>
<br>
Cons: If peeps raise by 1 auction can drag on (use a separate chat channel). Peeps can hoard points to buy cheaper later but so what, let em. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=151334">Pling, Maestro of AB</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lanolar>Lanolar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 908<br> <font color=#330000>(6/5/04 10:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19464.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ..</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I've let em rot till I have my Rizlona's bp / Quarm hammer (1st in line for both.)<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
