<br>
If you want an item you toss your name in a hat.<br>
<br>
the raid en mass rolls.  Highest roll chooses who in the hat wins.<br>
<br>
Its unbelievably good.  We typically consult attendance charts, loot charts, and even get input from officers and others as to class need etc.<br>
<br>
Teh impedious is on the guild then and not the officers.<br>
<br>
A particular person has chosen against me 6 times recently, and thats the downside.  If those that don't like you for some odd reason ...well, you understand.<br>
<br>
I'd recommend it to anyone, especially those that have resullts as the thread starter noted.<br>
