VT but didn't stop coming to raids so they just amassed points. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=169925">Impresario Cireon Nevelsmythe &lt;Gale of Destruction&gt;</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
